<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Login - Evil Capitalistic Corp</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>ğŸ” Secure Login</h1>
            <nav>
                <a href="/">ğŸ  Home</a>
                <a href="/register">ğŸ“ Register</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        
        <main style="padding: 3rem 2rem; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <div style="background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <h2 style="color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 2rem; text-align: center;">Login to Your Account</h2>
                
                <% if (error) { %>
                    <div style="background: #f8d7da; border: 2px solid #dc3545; color: #721c24; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 5px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                        <%= error %>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
                
                <form method="POST" action="/login">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                        <label style="display: block; color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Username</label>
                        <input type="text" name="username" required 
                               style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1rem;">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                        <label style="display: block; color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Password</label>
                        <input type="password" name="password" required 
                               style="width: 100%; padding: 0.75rem; border: 2px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1rem;">
                    </div>
                    
                    <button type="submit" style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd700, #ffed4e); border: none; border-radius: 5px; color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; cursor: pointer;">
                        Login
                    </button>
                </form>
                
                <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem; color: #666;">
                    Don't have an account? <a href="/register" style="color: #1a1a2e; font-weight: 600;">Register here</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #d1ecf1; border: 2px dashed #0c5460; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
                <p style="color: #0c5460; font-weight: 600;">ğŸ’¡ Hacker Hint:</p>
                <p style="color: #0c5460;">Try exploring other endpoints first. You might find some debug endpoints that reveal useful information about user accounts and their passwords...</p>
                <p style="color: #0c5460; margin-top: 0.5rem;"><strong>Hint:</strong> Check /debug/users</p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
